{"tid":1106282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國男港鐵站內偷銀包 熱心乘客合力制服","createTime":"2019-04-14T13:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T15:01:27.000Z","uid":39464,"like":236,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"6bc9240f2496af79e228e91f1f3a3e7e28499cb1","tid":1106282,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190414/large/1555243370_89e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190414%2Flarge%2F1555243370_89e8.jpg&h=5d0c5ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名雙程證扒手，下午在港鐵深水埗站人多搭扶手電梯，趁機扒竊一名印尼女傭的銀包被察覺，事主呼救，多名熱心乘客在扶梯上合力將扒手制服，糾纏間扶梯上一名男乘客被推跌受輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n被捕內地疑犯姓韋36歲，34歲印尼女事主，在港做家傭，現場為深水埗站往荃灣方向月台上行扶手電梯，今午4時許，事主孭住背囊與兩名女同鄉落地鐵後乘扶梯上大堂，韋尾隨事主，並扶梯上暗中打開事主背囊扒竊其銀包，事主發覺阻止並大聲呼叫，韋見事敗企圖逃走，被多名乘客前後合力阻止，雙方一度在扶梯上糾纏，其後韋終被制服，混亂中扶梯上一名男乘客被撞倒受輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者鄧先生稱，該名男子在移動中的扶梯上被多名乘客制服後，港鐵職員按停扶梯，眾乘客合力將疑犯拉落月台，由稍後到場警員押走。剛落車目睹事件何小姐亦謂，「個姐姐(印傭)事後攞番銀包，佢好驚，係咁喺度喊。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190414/large/1555243370_b47b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190414%2Flarge%2F1555243370_b47b.jpg&h=aaa1d207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉事印傭（箭嘴示）取回銀包後，不停大哭。讀者何小姐提供<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190414/59488312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190414%2F59488312&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvcTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=67d9e438\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190414%2F59488312&h=fed375ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190414/59488312</a>"},{"pid":"d69af7d7a1965478b68edec4ab6a593681fb391f","tid":1106282,"uid":178199,"like":201,"disli